{
  "meta": {
    "slug": "mulan-meets-mushu",
    "category": "movie",
    "source_url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=grbLjl1AjAs&t=3s",
    "mode": "cues_rebuild"
  },
  "dialogue": [
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Okay, okay, how about this?",
      "zh": "好，好，那這樣如何？",
      "ja": "はい、はい、これでどう？",
      "time": "00:00:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ugh.",
      "zh": "唉。",
      "ja": "うっ。",
      "time": "00:00:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Excuse me. Where do I sign it?",
      "zh": "不好意思，我在哪裡簽名？",
      "ja": "すみません。どこにサインすればいいですか？",
      "time": "00:00:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I see you have a sword. I have one too.",
      "zh": "我看到你有把劍，我也有一把。",
      "ja": "剣を持っているね。私も持っているよ。",
      "time": "00:00:08"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They're very madly.",
      "zh": "它們非常瘋狂。",
      "ja": "それらはとても激しい。",
      "time": "00:00:12"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm working on it.",
      "zh": "我正在努力。",
      "ja": "取り組んでいるところだ。",
      "time": "00:00:14"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Who am I fooling?",
      "zh": "我在騙誰？",
      "ja": "誰を騙しているんだ？",
      "time": "00:00:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "It's going to take a miracle to get me into the army.",
      "zh": "要我進軍隊，得靠奇蹟。",
      "ja": "私が軍隊に入るには奇跡が必要だ。",
      "time": "00:00:24"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I hear someone asked for a miracle.",
      "zh": "我聽到有人在求奇蹟。",
      "ja": "誰かが奇跡を求めていると聞いた。",
      "time": "00:00:27"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let me hear you say, ah!",
      "zh": "讓我聽你說，啊！",
      "ja": "さあ、あーと言ってみて！",
      "time": "00:00:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "That's close enough.",
      "zh": "這樣就差不多了。",
      "ja": "それで十分だ。",
      "time": "00:00:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Go!",
      "zh": "走！",
      "ja": "行け！",
      "time": "00:00:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Get ready, Malign.",
      "zh": "準備好，Malign。",
      "ja": "準備しろ、マリグン。",
      "time": "00:00:35"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "You're 17, South Asian.",
      "zh": "你17歲，南亞裔。",
      "ja": "君は17歳、南アジア出身だ。",
      "time": "00:00:36"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm going to get in.",
      "zh": "我要進去。",
      "ja": "私は入るつもりだ。",
      "time": "00:00:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I have been sent by your ancestors.",
      "zh": "我是你的祖先派來的。",
      "ja": "私は君の先祖に送られた。",
      "time": "00:00:38"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "To God through your mastery.",
      "zh": "通過你的精通給神。",
      "ja": "君の技を通じて神へ。",
      "time": "00:00:41"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Come on, you're going to stay.",
      "zh": "來吧，你會留下。",
      "ja": "さあ、君はここにいるんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:44"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're going to work.",
      "zh": "你會工作的。",
      "ja": "君は働くんだ。",
      "time": "00:00:45"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "So he's my word.",
      "zh": "所以這是我的承諾。",
      "ja": "だからこれは私の言葉だ。",
      "time": "00:00:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Go to the army.",
      "zh": "去軍隊。",
      "ja": "軍隊に行け。",
      "time": "00:00:48"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Find out your guard.",
      "zh": "找出你的守衛。",
      "ja": "君の守りを見つけろ。",
      "time": "00:00:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "The penalty is down.",
      "zh": "懲罰是倒下。",
      "ja": "罰は倒れることだ。",
      "time": "00:00:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who are you?",
      "zh": "你是誰？",
      "ja": "君は誰だ？",
      "time": "00:00:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Who am I?",
      "zh": "我是誰？",
      "ja": "私は誰だ？",
      "time": "00:00:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Who am I? Who am I?",
      "zh": "我是誰？我是誰？",
      "ja": "私は誰だ？私は誰だ？",
      "time": "00:00:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I am the guard in the lost holes.",
      "zh": "我是失落洞穴的守衛。",
      "ja": "私は失われた穴の守護者だ。",
      "time": "00:00:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I am the powerful, the plasherner.",
      "zh": "我是強大的，Plasherner。",
      "ja": "私は強力な、プラッシャーナーだ。",
      "time": "00:01:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "They're in the structure of the mousse.",
      "zh": "他們在慕斯的結構中。",
      "ja": "彼らはムースの構造の中にいる。",
      "time": "00:01:04"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Oh, I have to do it.",
      "zh": "哦，我得做。",
      "ja": "ああ、やらなきゃ。",
      "time": "00:01:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm not.",
      "zh": "我不是。",
      "ja": "私は違う。",
      "time": "00:01:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "My ancestors sent a little lizard to help me.",
      "zh": "我的祖先派了一隻小蜥蜴來幫助我。",
      "ja": "私の先祖は小さなトカゲを送って助けてくれた。",
      "time": "00:01:17"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Hey, dragon, dragon, not lizard.",
      "zh": "嘿，龍，龍，不是蜥蜴。",
      "ja": "ねえ、ドラゴン、ドラゴン、トカゲじゃない。",
      "time": "00:01:20"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I don't do that tongue thing.",
      "zh": "我不會那樣吐舌頭。",
      "ja": "あの舌を出すことはしない。",
      "time": "00:01:23"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "You're intimidating?",
      "zh": "你很嚇人嗎？",
      "ja": "怖がらせるつもり？",
      "time": "00:01:26"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "On, Spire?",
      "zh": "在尖塔上？",
      "ja": "尖塔の上？",
      "time": "00:01:29"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Tiny.",
      "zh": "小小的。",
      "ja": "小さい。",
      "time": "00:01:30"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Of course.",
      "zh": "當然。",
      "ja": "もちろん。",
      "time": "00:01:31"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm travel-sacced for your convenience.",
      "zh": "我為了你的方便而縮小。",
      "ja": "君のために縮小している。",
      "time": "00:01:32"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If I was my real size, you're cow here with that afraid.",
      "zh": "如果我是真實大小，你會嚇壞的。",
      "ja": "もし本当の大きさなら、君は怖がるだろう。",
      "time": "00:01:34"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Down, Bessie.",
      "zh": "下去，Bessie。",
      "ja": "おとなしくして、ベッシー。",
      "time": "00:01:37"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "If my power was I'd be on your model of imagination.",
      "zh": "如果我有力量，我會在你的想像中。",
      "ja": "もし力があれば、君の想像の中にいるだろう。",
      "time": "00:01:39"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "For instance, my eyes can see straight through your armor.",
      "zh": "例如，我的眼睛能看穿你的盔甲。",
      "ja": "例えば、私の目は君の鎧を貫いて見ることができる。",
      "time": "00:01:42"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Ow!",
      "zh": "哎呦！",
      "ja": "痛っ！",
      "time": "00:01:46"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right, that's it.",
      "zh": "好了，就這樣。",
      "ja": "よし、これで終わりだ。",
      "time": "00:01:47"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This honor.",
      "zh": "這份榮譽。",
      "ja": "この名誉。",
      "time": "00:01:49"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This honor on your whole family.",
      "zh": "這份榮譽屬於你全家。",
      "ja": "この名誉は君の家族全員に。",
      "time": "00:01:50"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I can know this.",
      "zh": "我能知道這點。",
      "ja": "私はこれを知っている。",
      "time": "00:01:52"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "This honor on you.",
      "zh": "這份榮譽屬於你。",
      "ja": "この名誉は君に。",
      "time": "00:01:53"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "This honor on your cow.",
      "zh": "這份榮譽屬於你的牛。",
      "ja": "この名誉は君の牛に。",
      "time": "00:01:54"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Stop!",
      "zh": "停下！",
      "ja": "やめろ！",
      "time": "00:01:55"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "zh": "對不起。",
      "ja": "ごめん。",
      "time": "00:01:56"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I'm sorry.",
      "zh": "對不起。",
      "ja": "ごめん。",
      "time": "00:01:57"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "I'm just nervous.",
      "zh": "我只是緊張。",
      "ja": "ただ緊張しているだけだ。",
      "time": "00:01:58"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "I've never done this before.",
      "zh": "我以前從沒做過這事。",
      "ja": "こんなことは初めてだ。",
      "time": "00:02:00"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Then you're going to have to trust me.",
      "zh": "那你得信任我。",
      "ja": "なら、私を信じなければならない。",
      "time": "00:02:01"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "And don't you slap me no more.",
      "zh": "別再打我了。",
      "ja": "もう私を叩かないで。",
      "time": "00:02:03"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "We clearly aren't there.",
      "zh": "我們顯然還沒到那裡。",
      "ja": "私たちは明らかにそこにいない。",
      "time": "00:02:05"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "All right.",
      "zh": "好吧。",
      "ja": "わかった。",
      "time": "00:02:06"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Okay, now get this show in the road.",
      "zh": "好，現在開始吧。",
      "ja": "よし、さあ始めよう。",
      "time": "00:02:07"
    },
    {
      "role": "teacher",
      "text": "Tricky, get the bags.",
      "zh": "Tricky，拿包包。",
      "ja": "トリッキー、バッグを取って。",
      "time": "00:02:09"
    },
    {
      "role": "student",
      "text": "Let's move it half up.",
      "zh": "我們快點行動。",
      "ja": "さあ、急ごう。",
      "time": "00:02:10"
    }
  ]
}